{"updated_at": "2012-10-12T15:11:00Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2012-10-12T15:11:00Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/9379561", "id": 9379561, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7913", "issue_id": 7913, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/jwinter", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "bc5e12d93ec9bbda6ec8f81001d45ba7", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/bc5e12d93ec9bbda6ec8f81001d45ba7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ffe2d010308a6b3799a3d9c728ee74244.png", "id": 1200, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/events{/privacy}", "login": "jwinter", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jwinter/followers"}, "body": "You can see where the additional 5.minutes used to be added to the expires_in sent to memcached here: https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/a02b40a3d28c4b262dd49a8a6166c0275dfd9964/activesupport/lib/active_support/cache/mem_cache_store.rb#L142\r\nWithout that padding, there will never be a window where both your entry is expired (via its expired_at) and memcached still has its value, so you'll never be able to serve the cached value to the other readers.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f7bcbd3543c15100b10b"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7913#issuecomment-9379561"}
